Interface ChatIF

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseMenuController, CardReaderView, EditSubscriberDetailsController, ManagerDashboardController, ManageReservationController, ManageTablesController, NewReservationController, OccasionalLoginController, OccasionalMenuController, OccasionalRegistrationController, PayBillEntryController, PaymentUIController, RemoteLoginController, RepresentativeDashboardController, ReservationHistoryController, SubscriberLoginController, SubscriberMenuController, TerminalLoginController, TerminalMenuController, TerminalWaitingListSizeController, ViewReservationController, VisitUIController
public interface ChatIF
The ChatIF interface defines the communication contract for the Client-side User Interface (UI) in the Bistro system. Any class acting as a UI layer must implement this interface to receive data asynchronously from the server.
